## One-liner PowerShell to write both files now

From `C:\Users\tahaz\seaweed`:

```powershell
# .gitignore
@'
# --- Node / tooling ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.nyc_output/
coverage/
*.lcov

# --- Build / caches / temp ---
dist/
build/
.tmp/
temp/
tmp/
.cache/

# --- OS / editors ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Logs / pids ---
logs/
*.log
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# --- Environment / secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Local data volumes ---
data/
mongo-data/
redis-data/
pg-data/
dump.rdb

# --- Video/stream artifacts ---
hls/
*.m3u8
*.ts

# --- NGINX temp dirs ---
client_body_temp/
proxy_temp/
fastcgi_temp/
uwsgi_temp/
scgi_temp/
'@ | Set-Content -Encoding UTF8 .gitignore

# README.md
@'
# seaweed (buttblastr core)

**Author:** taha z  
**Repo:** https://github.com/baja1223/seaweed

[...snip: copy the full README content from above block ...]
'@ | Set-Content -Encoding UTF8 README.md
